<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>A local institution. No pretense, no social media gloss, no trendy interior. Just very careful sourcing, meticulous attention to cooking and ingredients, and honest prices. The kind of place where regulars come back every week.</p>
    <p>The collaboration started with Emmanuel, who handled all the video production side. My focus was on brand and digital presence, always keeping the no-fuss identity intact.</p>
